    ["Penalty for travelling without pass or ticket and for dereliction of duty on the part of conductor and refusal to ply contract carriage, etc.","3) (a) Shall be punishable with fine, which may extend to Rs. 50/- for 2 or 3 wheeler M.V. and (b) Shall be punishable with fine may extend to Rs. 200/- in any other case."],
