    ["Allowing unauthorized persons to drive vehicles.","Shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term which may extend to THREE MONTHS, or with fine which may extend to Rs. 100/-, or with both."],
    ["Driving vehicles in contravention of section 3 or section 4.","Shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term which may extend to THREE MONTHS, or with fine which may extend to Rs. 500/-, or with both."],
    ["Offence relating to licenses.","1) Shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term which may extend to THREE MONTHS, or with fine which may extend to Rs. 500/-, or with both and any driving licence so obtained by him shall be of no effect."],
